  <refsection xml:id='examples'>
    <title>EXAMPLES</title>
    
    <example><title>Object Summary</title>

      <para>
        <prompt>mged&gt; </prompt><userinput>brep Brep_1.s info</userinput>
        <literallayout class="normal">
Brep_1.s -- Valid: YES, Solid: YES, Plate mode: NO
faces:     597
surfaces:  597
edges:     1475
3d curve:  1475
vertices:  976
loops:     715
trims:     3056
2d curves: 3056
        </literallayout>
      </para>
      <para>
        Reports counts for the various object types, as well as object
        level info about solidity, validity and plate mode status.
      </para>
    </example>

